{
  "texts": [
    "The CELLO dataset comprises 523 English directives, all derived from data manually curated in real-world situations.",
    "Its principal objective is to gauge the proficiency of LLMs in comprehending intricate instructions.",
    "The evaluation encompasses ten subtasks, addressing aspects related to both complex task description and complex input.",
    "The evaluation methodology employs code assessment.",
    "• MT-Bench (Zheng et al, 2023b)."
  ]
}